query:
SELECT e.id, e.turmaId, e.tipoEvento, 
       e.dataEvento, e.dataEventoFim,
       UNIX_TIMESTAMP(e.dataEvento) as timestamp_inicio,
       UNIX_TIMESTAMP(e.dataEventoFim) as timestamp_fim,
       e.local, l.nome as localNome
FROM eventos e
LEFT JOIN locais l ON e.local = l.id
WHERE e.turmaId IN (
  SELECT id FROM turmas 
  WHERE cursos LIKE '%MEDICINA%' AND instituicoes LIKE '%UPE%' AND numeroTurma = '115'
)
ORDER BY e.tipoEvento, e.dataEvento;
